# Python-License

Vehicle licensing app built with Python and Streamlit.

## Overview
This project helps automate parts of the vehicle licensing process by collecting user details, generating supporting documents, and handling PDF workflows.

## Features
- Streamlit-based interface
- PDF generation and merging
- Permission letter creation
- Form automation workflow

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- PyPDF
- ReportLab
- python-docx

## Files
- `app.py` – main application logic
- `requirements.txt` – dependencies
- `forms/` – supporting files and templates

## Why I Built It
I wanted to solve a real admin-heavy problem by building a practical Python application that reduces manual form work.
